### Notification API Test Requests
### RESTful API endpoints following RESTful standards
### 
### Prerequisites:
### 1. Make sure the server is running (default: http://localhost:3000)
### 2. You need to be authenticated (session cookie required)
### 3. For authentication, you may need to login first via /api/auth endpoints

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### Variables (update these with your actual values)
@notificationId = 1
@sessionCookie = your-session-cookie-here

###############################################
### NOTIFICATIONS RESOURCE
###############################################

### GET /api/notifications
### Get notifications for authenticated user (with pagination)
### Query params: page (default: 1), limit (default: 20), unreadOnly (boolean, default: false)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Cookie: connect.sid={{sessionCookie}}

###

### GET /api/notifications (With pagination)
### Get notifications with custom pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Cookie: connect.sid={{sessionCookie}}

###

### GET /api/notifications (Unread only)
### Get only unread notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?unreadOnly=true
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Cookie: connect.sid={{sessionCookie}}

###

### GET /api/notifications (Page 2)
### Get second page of notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?page=2&limit=20
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Cookie: connect.sid={{sessionCookie}}

###

### GET /api/notifications/unread-count
### Get unread notification count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/unread-count
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Cookie: connect.sid={{sessionCookie}}

###

### PATCH /api/notifications/read-all
### Mark all notifications as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/read-all
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Cookie: connect.sid={{sessionCookie}}

{}

###

### PATCH /api/notifications/:notificationId/read
### Mark a specific notification as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/{{notificationId}}/read
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Cookie: connect.sid={{sessionCookie}}

{}

###

### PATCH /api/notifications/:notificationId/read (Invalid - notification not found)
### Should return 404 Not Found
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/99999/read
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Cookie: connect.sid={{sessionCookie}}

{}

